  "script": [
    {
      "speaker": "narrator",
      "text": "여기는 우리 집 마당이에요. 마당에는 오렌지 나무가 있어요.",
      "en": "This is our backyard. There is an orange tree in the yard.",
      "slide": 0
    },
    {
      "speaker": "narrator",
      "text": "저는 동생하고 마당에서 배구를 해요.",
      "en": "I'm playing volleyball with my sibling in the yard.",
      "slide": 1
    },
    {
      "speaker": "na",
      "text": "내 공 받아!",
      "en": "Catch my ball!",
      "speech_type": "반말",
      "audio": "data/nhs/TTS/ep2/1내공+받아_slide2.mp3",
      "slide": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "dongsaeng",
      "text": "알았어!",
      "en": "Got it!",
      "speech_type": "반말",
      "audio": "data/nhs/TTS/ep2/2알았어_slide2.mp3",
      "slide": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "narrator",
      "text": "엄마가 우리를 불러요.",
      "en": "Mom calls us.",
      "slide": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "mom",
      "text": "얘들아~ 밥 먹어!",
      "en": "Kids~ time to eat!",
      "speech_type": "반말",
      "audio": "data/nhs/TTS/ep2/3얘들아~+밥+먹어slide3.mp3",
      "slide": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "narrator",
      "text": "모두 저녁 밥을 먹어요.",
      "en": "Everyone eats dinner.",
      "slide": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "mom",
      "text": "모두들 맛있게 먹어요.",
      "en": "Everyone, enjoy your meal!",
      "speech_type": "casual 존댓말",
      "audio": "data/nhs/TTS/ep2/4모두들+맛있게+먹어요slide5.mp3",
      "slide": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "dongsaeng",
      "text": "잘 먹겠습니다!",
      "en": "Thank you for the food! (before eating)",
      "speech_type": "존댓말",
      "audio": "data/nhs/TTS/ep2/5잘+먹겠습니다slide5.mp3",
      "slide": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "na",
      "text": "잘 먹겠습니다!",
      "en": "Thank you for the food! (before eating)",
      "speech_type": "존댓말",
      "audio": "data/nhs/TTS/ep2/6잘+먹겠습니다slide5.mp3",
      "slide": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "na",
      "text": "엄마, 이거 너무 맛있어요!",
      "en": "Mom, this is so delicious!",
      "speech_type": "존댓말",
      "audio": "data/nhs/TTS/ep2/7엄마이거너무맛있어요slide6.mp3",
      "slide": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "dongsaeng",
      "text": "잘 먹었습니다, 엄마!",
      "en": "Thank you for the meal, Mom!",
      "speech_type": "존댓말",
      "audio": "data/nhs/TTS/ep2/8잘+먹었습니다+엄마slide7.mp3",
      "slide": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "na",
      "text": "잘 먹었습니다, 엄마!",
      "en": "Thank you for the meal, Mom!",
      "speech_type": "존댓말",
      "audio": "data/nhs/TTS/ep2/9잘+먹었습니다+엄마slide7.mp3",
      "slide": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "dad",
      "text": "나도 잘 먹었어요.",
      "en": "I enjoyed the meal too.",
      "speech_type": "casual 존댓말",
      "audio": "data/nhs/TTS/ep2/10나도+잘+먹었어요slide7.mp3",
      "slide": 7
    }
